    "body": "For monetizing, there's nothing in any free software license preventing it. Just, monetization cannot come from selling the code, because anybody can get it for free. I think this is the only way in which software could work, everything else is broken and unsustainable. \r\n\r\nAs mentioned in our [internal discussion](https://collective.flashbots.net/t/make-the-relay-free-software/78/16), I don’t think our competitive advantage should rely on private code at all.",
